name: SSA-719
Lore: 'Security battle droid assigned to quell uprisings before they have a chance to gather momentum. Believes the best form of defense is offense.',
Text: 'While with another battle droid, power +3. If with a battle droid on Naboo and you just verified opponent''s Reserve Deck, may lose 2 Force to search that Reserve Deck and place one card you find there out of play.',
